  "remarks": "Son of Usama bin Laden (deceased).  Announced by Aiman Muhammed Rabi al-Zawahiri (QDi.006) as an official member of Al-Qaida (QDe.004). Has called for follwers of Al-Qaida to commit terror attacks.  Was seen as the most probable successor of al-Zawahiri. Reportedly killed in a counterterrorism operation as of September 2019 in the Afghanistan/Pakistan region.; Listing: Listed on: 28 Feb. 2019 (amended on 13 Mar. 2019, 11 Mar. 2025)",
